OL,3,CMarian Beattie's family 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover review into murder investigation
OL,6,FThe family of Marian Beattie have said
OL,7,Fthey are "frustrated" after the PSNI
OL,8,FChief Constable commissioned an
OL,9,Findependent peer review into the
OL,10,Fmurder investigation just hours after
OL,11,Fmeeting the first minister.
OL,13,FMs Beattie was found dead at the
OL,14,Fbottom of a quarry in Aughnacloy in Co
OL,15,FTyrone in 1973.
OL,17,FThe Portadown teenager's killer has
OL,18,Fnever been caught in the more than 50
OL,19,Fyears since her death.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
