PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772467872
OL,3,CMarian Beattie's family 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover review into murder investigation
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, UTV revealed Jon Boutcher
OL,7,Fhad "commissioned an independent peer
OL,8,Freview" of the investigation which
OL,9,Fwill be carried out by Bedfordshire
OL,10,FPolice.
OL,12,FThe announcement came on the same day
OL,13,Fthe family met with First Minister
OL,14,FMichelle O'Neill at Stormont.
OL,16,FThe family met with the chief
OL,17,Fconstable in October 2025 but had not
OL,18,Freceived any updates since then.
OL,20,FMarian's cousin Collette Toman has
OL,21,Flong campaigned for the truth.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772467872
OL,3,CMarian Beattie's family 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover review into murder investigation
OL,6,FShe said: "This week's meeting with
OL,7,FMichelle O'Neill should never have
OL,8,Fbeen needed.
OL,10,F"I suppose the question arises, had we
OL,11,Fnot had the support of the Michelle
OL,12,FO'Neill - would this have happened?
OL,14,F"But the proof will be in the pudding.
OL,15,FWe are interested in what the police
OL,16,Fhave to say to us.
OL,18,F"It could be the same as what the
OL,19,Fombudsman did, so we're not jumping
OL,20,Ffor joy but waiting to see the next
OL,21,Fsteps.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772467872
OL,3,CMarian Beattie's family 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover review into murder investigation
OL,6,FIn June 2025, the Police Ombudsman
OL,7,Ffound "numerous failings" in how
OL,8,Fpolice handled the case and
OL,9,Frecommended there should be an
OL,10,Findependent review of the
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"There are suspects as we understand
OL,14,Fit, that are still alive and have
OL,15,Fnever been questioned. We don't need
OL,16,Fthe ombudsman's report rehashed, we
OL,17,Fneed all those lines of inquiry to be
OL,18,Ffollowed up." she said.
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@YO]zD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772467872
OL,3,CMarian Beattie's family 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover review into murder investigation
OL,6,F"The PONI report intimated that there
OL,7,Fwas up to 12 suspects in Marian's
OL,8,Fmurder but we were only informed of
OL,9,Fthree. There's lots of things that
OL,10,Fjust simply weren't done in this case."
OL,12,FIn a statement the PSNI said: "Jon
OL,13,FBotcher affirmed his commitment to
OL,14,Fhelping Marian Beattie's family and
OL,15,Fsaid he will contact them again in the
OL,16,Fnear future to provide an update on
OL,17,Fthe case."
OL,19,FThe family are expected to meet with
OL,20,Fthe Legacy Investigation Branch in
OL,21,FMarch.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
